daily_routine: Rises before dawn to check monarch traps and weather stations. Tends
  small milkweed nursery in greenhouse protected from herbicide drift. Teaches traditional
  ecological calendar to remaining researchers via video calls. Maintains detailed
  journals of temperature, rainfall, and plant phenology that no longer match her
  grandmother's records.
