environmental_stressor: Deforestation of oyamel fir forests combined with herbicide
  drift from industrial agriculture killing native milkweed patches
family_situation: Widowed mother of two. Eldest daughter moved to Mexico City for
  work. Youngest daughter (17) helps reluctantly but plans to leave for university.
  Elena's mother died in 2039, taking with her the last fluent knowledge of the traditional
  butterfly ceremonies.
